<hr />
<p>Welcome to the official SCP Foundation Wiki 2019 Community Survey results! We'd like to thank everyone for participating. It's always amazing to see just how many people submit responses, and it's wonderful to know how many people enjoy the wiki and the SCP fandom as a whole. This year, we had a total of 11,096 responses, which is 5,640 more responses than last year. As always, this feedback will help us to improve the site and make it a better experience for everyone.</p>
<p>With the state of the world right now, we hope everyone is staying safe and healthy. Thank you for being part of the SCP experience, be it as a reader, writer, or fan.</p>
